data.description: BRING YOUR LIVESTOCK AND HORSES! Welcome to an exceptional opportunity to own over 7 acres of prime land nestled in the picturesque countryside of Callahan, Florida. This property boasts a 3BR/2B home that has laminated wood floors throughout, a large garden tub with split bedrooms. The spacious living room offers many windows for natural light. Enjoy your 4 Stall barn with a tack room and make this place yours with endless opportunities to make it your own.
